{"tid":756064,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"林宥嘉首新歌 脆弱一分鐘好好聽呀屌","createTime":"2018-07-25T16:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T06:53:04.000Z","uid":16425,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"923c3e037aa8d0b9ec40b3dfb8bab8208aec68f1","tid":756064,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ozNEA0KgKIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FozNEA0KgKIQ&d=SYmISraU9ZlyjAGhV3twAjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d81ee5a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ozNEA0KgKIQ</a><br />\n<br />\n誰也不要走 應該是一種奢求<br />\n可是我只想 握緊你的手<br />\n我寧願等候 也不願錯過<br />\n你對我微笑的時候<br />\n<br />\n還是願意 用盡全力僅僅為了一個以後<br />\n哪怕生命並不溫柔 哪怕被幸福一再反駁<br />\n也要相信傷痕累累 其實只是在琢磨<br />\n能讓你為之一亮的我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4088d8ea79e40da7c5b6d4f0fbeb89d161834066","tid":756064,"uid":70711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"還是願意<br />\n用盡全力僅僅為了一個以後<br />\n哪怕生命並不溫柔 哪怕被幸福一再反駁<br />\n也要相信傷痕累累 其實只是在琢磨<br />\n能讓你為之一亮 的我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bea5581e7027dad43bb22f187a48cb3552a36e5","tid":756064,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得  佢結左婚之後  依首歌個演繹無左 「我總是一個人在練習一個人」 個寂寞mood 喎"},{"pid":"165415dc918d9173af1dc36dd6ef61b2bc05a15f","tid":756064,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"普通左啲"},{"pid":"be9a24cdfd15a7fc830aec7f432e9bc643c75b15","tid":756064,"uid":70711,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8bea5581e7027dad43bb22f187a48cb3552a36e5","tid":756064,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl